                    <i data-lucide="truck" class="w-10 h-10 text-brand-gold mx-auto mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy text-sm mb-1">お墓のお引っ越し無料相談</h3>
                    <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mb-4">お見積りや手続きについてお答えします</p>
                    <a href="#booking" class="block w-full py-2.5 px-4 bg-brand-navy hover:bg-brand-gold text-white text-xs font-bold rounded-xl transition-all">
